Type: Package
Package: mutrisk
Title: Package to estimate the number of mutated cells across tissues
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Axel", "Rosendahl Huber", , "axel.rosendahl@irbbarcelona.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Package can be used to model the mutation density across
    tissues and individuals.  These densities for single patients, or
    cells can be used to estimate the mutation load
